quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  7,100,"Kodi m’badwo uno, umene wadza pambuyo pa wina, siuzindikira kuti ngati Ife titafuna, tikhoza kuulanga chifukwa cha machimo awo? Ndipo timaika chimatiro m’mitima mwawo kuti asamve"
  7,101,Imeneyo ndi mizinda imene nkhani zake tili kukuuza iwe. Ndithudi kudadza kwa iwo Atumwi awo ndi zizindikiro zooneka. Koma iwo sadakhulupirire zimene adazikana kale. Kotero Mulungu amamata mitima ya anthu osakhulupirira
  7,102,"Ife sitidaone ambiri mwa iwo amene adasunga malonjezo koma Ife tidawapeza, ndithudi, ambiri a iwo ali anthu ochita zoipa"
  7,103,"Atapita awa, Ife tidatumiza Mose ndi zizindikiro zathu kwa Farao ndi mafumu ake koma iwo adazikana. Motero taona mapeto a anthu ochita zoipa"
  7,104,"Ndipo Mose adati: “oh Farao! Ine ndine Mtumwi wochokera kwa Ambuye wazolengedwa zonse"
  7,105,Ndithudi ine sindidzanena china chilichonse chokhudza Mulungu kupatula choonadi. Ndithudi ine ndakubweretserani chizindikiro chosakaikitsa kuchokera kwa Ambuye wanu. Motero alole ana a Israyeli kuti apite ndi ine.”
  7,106,"Farao adati: “Ngati wabwera ndi chizindikiro, chionetse msanga ngati uli kunena zoona.”"
  7,107,Ndipo Mose adaponya pansi ndodo yake ndipo nthawi yomweyo idasanduka njoka yeniyeni
  7,108,Ndipo iye adatulutsa dzanja lake ndipo nthawi yomweyo lidasanduka loyera kwa iwo amene adaliona